Media
Light novel
Written by Kaitō, ''A Nobody's Way Up to an Exploration Hero'' began serialization on the user-generated novel publishing website Shōsetsuka ni Narō on April 9, 2019. It was later acquired by Hobby Japan who began releasing it under their HJ Bunko imprint with illustrations by Almic in July 2021. Twelve volumes have been released as of September 1, 2025.
